            "id": 6247422,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 羅斯百貨(ROST-US)大漲5.6%，報169.49美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>羅斯百貨(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ROST:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ROST\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ROST-US</a>)截至台北時間21日22:30股價上漲8.99美元，報169.49美元，漲幅5.6%，成交量352,691（股），盤中最高價169.49美元、最低價163.51美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.53%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.51%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.35%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.02%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>羅斯百貨(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ROST:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ROST\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ROST-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-0.85%</li> <li>近 1 月：+1.91%</li> <li>近 3 月：+9.63%</li> <li>近 6 月：+4.03%</li> <li>今年以來：+5.14%</li></ul></section></main>",
